  "hashtags" : [ ],
  "sections" : [ {
    "type" : "verse",
    "label" : "VERSE 1",
    "lines" : [ {
      "text" : "It only takes a spark to get a fire going,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 3
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 16
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 25
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 31
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 36
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "And soon all those around can warm up in its glowing,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 4
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 20
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 30
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 38
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 45
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "That's how it is with God's love,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 7
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 22
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "Once you've experienced it,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 5
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 16
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 24
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "You spread His love to everyone,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 4
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 15
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 23
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "You want to pass it on !",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 4
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 12
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 20
      } ]
    } ]
  }, {
    "type" : "verse",
    "label" : "VERSE 2",
    "lines" : [ {
      "text" : "What a wondrous time is spring, when all the trees are budding,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 7
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 24
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 37
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 45
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 55
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "The birds begin to sing, the flowers start their blooming.",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 4
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 19
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 29
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 37
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 49
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "That's how it is with God's love,"
    }, {
      "text" : "Once you've experienced it,"
    }, {
      "text" : "You want to sing-it's fresh like spring,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 4
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 12
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 22
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "You want to pass it on !"
    } ]
  }, {
    "type" : "verse",
    "label" : "VERSE 3",
    "lines" : [ {
      "text" : "I wish for you my friend, this happiness that I've found,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 2
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 18
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 31
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 36
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 46
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "You can depend on Him, it matters not where you're bound.",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 4
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 10
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 18
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 26
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 44
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "I'll shout it from the mountain top,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 5
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 23
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "I want the world to know.",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 2
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 11
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 20
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "The Lord of love has come to me,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 4
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 12
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 21
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "I want to pass it on !",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 2
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 10
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 18
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "(Repeat from 'I'll shout it......')"
    } ]
  } ]
}